name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fresh Inbox: Clean Gmail with Total Privacy

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Your go-to Chrome extension for a clutter-free Gmail experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to Fresh Inbox,
Q. Unwanted newsletters? 
Fresh Inbox can bid them farewell with its handy unsubscribe feature. 
Q. Tired of manually sifting through hundreds of emails? 
You can obliterate them all with just a single click, leaving your inbox refreshed.

✌️ Unsubscribe from newsletter & unwanted emails
🧹 1 Click bulk delete of 100/1000s of emails
🔒 No data ever leaves your browser
🌏 Free & Open Source

Say goodbye to email overwhelm with FreshInbox.
